OL,3,CHomeowner frustrated as bus driver
OL,4,Ctoilet placed outside home
OL,6,FA man from south London says his
OL,7,Fattempts to sell his home have hit a
OL,8,Fmajor obstacle - a toilet, installed
OL,9,Fright outside his house for bus
OL,10,Fdrivers.
OL,12,FBrett Kemp, who lives at the end of a
OL,13,Fbus route in Purley, has been left
OL,14,Ffrustrated by Transport for London's
OL,15,F(TfL) decision to place the temporary
OL,16,Flavatory next to his property.
OL,18,FHe is trying to sell his home, but
OL,19,Fsays he has only had two viewings in
OL,20,Fthe last three weeks.
