OL,3,CHomeowner frustrated as bus driver
OL,4,Ctoilet placed outside home
OL,6,FThe grey shed, which houses the
OL,7,Ftoilet, stands just yards from Mr
OL,8,FKemp's front door.
OL,10,FSpeaking to ITV News London, Mr Kemp
OL,11,Fsaid: "I came back from holiday in mid-
OL,12,FJuly and noticed there was a temporary
OL,13,Fstructure outside my other property. I
OL,14,Fdidn't think anything of it, as just
OL,15,Fthought it was a temporary structure.
OL,17,F"After a couple of weeks, it was still
OL,18,Fthere, so I parked up and viewed the
OL,19,Foutbuilding. This did not look
OL,20,Ftemporary as there is a concrete base.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
