OL,3,CHomeowner frustrated as bus driver
OL,4,Ctoilet placed outside home
OL,6,F"I then took a couple of weeks to try
OL,7,Fand find out who was responsible for
OL,8,Fthe toilet, as it seemed Croydon
OL,9,FCouncil were unaware of this, and with
OL,10,Fhelp from Gayle Gander (the local
OL,11,Fcouncillor), she found out it was TfL
OL,12,Fwho erected the toilet under permitted
OL,13,Fdevelopment, so no planning
OL,14,Fapplication was applied for to Croydon
OL,15,FCouncil."
OL,17,FMr Kemp told ITV News that TfL did not
OL,18,Fnotify any of the residents that the
OL,19,Ftoilet was going to be erected. He
OL,20,Fmade a formal complaint in August.
