OL,4,Ctoilet placed outside home
OL,6,FHe said: "...It's affecting me
OL,7,Fimmensely - a very stressful emotional
OL,8,Fand financial situation for me."
OL,10,FA spokesperson for the transport
OL,11,Fauthority said, "It's really important
OL,12,Fthat bus drivers are able to access
OL,13,Ftoilet facilities while working and
OL,14,Fthese play a vital role in enabling
OL,15,Feveryone to travel safely. We are
OL,16,Falways mindful of local residents when
OL,17,Fwe install these facilities and choose
OL,18,Flocations near the end of a bus route
OL,19,Fthat are most appropriate, taking into
OL,20,Faccount the need for access to
OL,21,Fpavements to be maintained.
