OL,6,F"This is a temporary facility
OL,7,Finstalled as an interim measure while
OL,8,Fa permanent location can be identified
OL,9,Fand TfL is currently working with
OL,10,FCroydon Council to investigate the
OL,11,Fpossibility of moving the temporary
OL,12,Ffacility or building a permanent
OL,13,Ffacility at a different nearby
OL,14,Flocation."
OL,16,FFor now, though, the toilet remains,
OL,17,Fmuch to Mr Kemp's frustration.
